oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmie Rodger's Rejects Tape 1 of 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recordings are of a variety of studio recordings of Jimmie Rodgers (musician). The accompanying band is unidentified. Additionally, the dates of recording are unidentified. The tracks are labeled as rejected takes by Jimmie Rodgers. The tape is part one of two. [explicit]
